<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
This directive sets the the address the server will bind to, no other
IPs are bound to when this directive is in effect.  This has the side
effect of making all &lt;VirtualHost&gt; blocks redundant.  All
configuration must be within the server context when this directive is
in effect.
</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>See also</title>
